1. AI-Powered EDA Tool Workflow (Start to End)

Description

This diagram illustrates the complete operational workflow of the AI-Powered EDA Tool from system startup to waveform visualization.

Key Highlights
Launching terminal and Ollama LLM server
Running backend Flask/Python application
Accessing secure local HTTPS web interface
Uploading Verilog RTL code
Executing automated EDA pipeline
Generating:
Circuit Diagrams
FSM Diagrams
Truth Tables
AI Analysis Summary
PPA Estimates
Waveform Outputs
Purpose

Provides users with an end-to-end understanding of how the tool operates during real-time execution.

